# PostgreSQL

> The world's most advanced open-source relational database. Powers enterprise applications with ACID compliance, JSON support, and extensive extensibility.

---

## Overview

PostgreSQL (Postgres) is an object-relational database system with over 35 years of active development. It's known for reliability, feature robustness, and performance.

### Why PostgreSQL?

| Feature | Benefit |
|---------|---------|
| **ACID Compliance** | Guaranteed data integrity |
| **JSON/JSONB** | NoSQL flexibility with SQL power |
| **Full-Text Search** | Built-in search without external tools |
| **Extensions** | pgvector for AI, PostGIS for geo, etc. |
| **Concurrency** | MVCC for high read/write workloads |

