## Key Concepts

### Data Types

```sql
-- Common types we use
id          UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid()
created_at  TIMESTAMP WITH TIME ZONE DEFAULT NOW()
metadata    JSONB
status      TEXT CHECK (status IN ('active', 'archived'))
```

### Indexing Strategy

```sql
-- B-tree for equality/range (default)
CREATE INDEX idx_rounds_user ON rounds(user_id);

-- GIN for JSONB queries
CREATE INDEX idx_rounds_metadata ON rounds USING GIN(metadata);

-- Partial index for common filters
CREATE INDEX idx_active_rounds ON rounds(user_id) WHERE status = 'active';
```

### Transactions

```sql
BEGIN;
  INSERT INTO rounds (...) VALUES (...);
  UPDATE users SET rounds_count = rounds_count + 1 WHERE id = $1;
COMMIT;
```

