## Common Operations

### Backup/Restore

```bash
# Backup
pg_dump -h localhost -U postgres -d lazygolfing > backup.sql

# Restore
psql -h localhost -U postgres -d lazygolfing < backup.sql
```

### Migration (via Prisma)

```bash
npx prisma migrate dev --name add_challenges_table
npx prisma migrate deploy  # Production
```

